DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$b = random(2,5,1);
$b1= $b + 1;
$c = random(2,5,1);
$c1= $c + 1;
$d = random(1,7,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Factor the polynomial \(y^{$b}(y+$d)^{$c}+y^{$b1}(y+$d)^{$c1}\). 
Your answer can be written as
\(y^r(y+A)^s(y^2+By+C)\) with \(r\), \(s\) \(A\), \( B\), and \(C \)- integers
$BR where \(r\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(s\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $c;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(A\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $d;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(B\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $d;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(C\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  1;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
